Usage: TALIB(MACD, INPUT_ARRAY, FAST_PERIOD, SLOW_PERIOD, TRIGGER_PERIOD, PLOT)
Description: Moving Average Convergence Divergence PLOT is an integer that specifies 1 of 3 plots available. Plot #1 is the MACD. Plot #2 is the trigger. Plot #3 is the oscillator.
